QuestData.Title: The Scent for a Brutosaur
QuestData.Description: Mood is everything for love, and Maka'fon is not in de mood. $b$bVoodoo incense, specially formulated for brutosaurs by an expert witch doctor like myself, will surely spark de fire of de mother spirit in her heart. $b$bCertain fragrant rushes work best, and de jungle will provide. $b$bZandalari rushes grow near de waters here. Get a good amount for me and I will make an incense bundle big enough to set de mood.
QuestData.LogDescription: Find $1oa Fragrant Rushes to make incense for Irritable Maka'fon.
